					<h1>Web Design Articles &#038; Tutorials</h1>
					<div class="intro">
					   <p>One of our goals at <a href="about.php">Scratchmedia</a> is "Everyone's web site works". We're working towards a world where all web sites are pleasant, easy, and appealing to use.</p>
<p>Since 2004, Ben Hunt has been posting articles and tutorials on all aspects of web design and production, sharing his particular insights into what makes web sites work.</p>
<p>Web Design from Scratch is an invaluable resource for anyone interested in web design, visited by millions of people worldwide.</p>
<p>Browse the categories in the menu to find a host of information to help you make better web sites.</p>					</div>
				</div>
